{"tid":94203,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[台服] 黑色沙漠 討論區 #2","createTime":"2017-01-25T05:00:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-03T08:36:58.000Z","uid":58683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"45c92b2002eb78ac14ea091b2078fd90eb2dfd43","tid":94203,"uid":58683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T05:00:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LQXf120ZKFg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLQXf120ZKFg&d=JLp0aZeKgaDJxHa8AUPXkWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=95c1c5eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LQXf120ZKFg</a><br />\n<br />\n官網 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.blackdesert.com.tw/main/index \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.blackdesert.com.tw%2Fmain%2Findex%20&d=JLp0aZeKgaDJxHa8AUPXkWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=c032e4cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.blackdesert.com.tw/main/index </a><br />\n<br />\n香港公會:<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">攻略組</span><br />\n半休閒公會， 已有9x 人， 會員大部份都香港<br />\n每日都有公會任，得閒可以幫手，<br />\n公會戰<br />\n會一齊王<br />\n<br />\n想入公會係GAME 密以下<br />\n好瘋狂<br />\n什麼樣子的道理啊<br />\nRaigatto<br />\n<br />\n或去以下 discord 公頻<br />\n@瘋叔叔<br />\n@Bubbly<br />\n@⚡IAmTheFlash_石仔⚡<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">從零開始</span><br />\n<br />\n休閒公會<br />\n想入公會係GAME 密以下<br />\n各掃自家門前雪<br />\n<br />\n或去以下 discord 公頻<br />\n@老男人<br />\n<br />\n(可以係GAME 公會排名睇返公會會長ID)<br />\n<br />\nLIHKG 公開 Discord 頻<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/PFWa8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2FPFWa8&d=JLp0aZeKgaDJxHa8AUPXkWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=b4b7580e\" target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/PFWa8</a><br />\n<br />\nQA<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. 隻game係唔係免費？</span><br />\n唔係, 買斷制, 要俾1次錢<br />\n現時有2個價, USD 32 , USD 10.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2. 港台服? 多唔多人玩？<br />\n</span>呢個係國際服(冇封地區IP), 但主要都係港台人玩(因為主要係繁中)...<br />\n好多人玩!<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3. USD 32 ,  USD 10 有咩分別!?</span><br />\nUSD 32 就 18/1 開始玩得.<br />\nUSD 10 就 25/1 先可以玩.<br />\n另外有咩可以去以下官方LINK 睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://payment.blackdesert.com.tw/Pay/Package/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpayment.blackdesert.com.tw%2FPay%2FPackage%2F&d=JLp0aZeKgaDJxHa8AUPXkWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=d47773cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://payment.blackdesert.com.tw/Pay/Package/</a><br />\n<br />\nUSD 32 包道具介紹(我都係新人, 講錯勿屌)<br />\n<br />\n角色欄位擴張一格券<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">可以開多個角色, 唔係就要買點</span><br />\n<br />\n價值禮包(30日)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">(有用, VIP, 兩個包都有)</span><br />\n<br />\n艾爾利恩之淚11個<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">(死左復活用)</span><br />\n<br />\n專業勞工契約包<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">(玩勞工用, 我岩岩開始玩生活, 未清楚有幾大效用)</span><br />\n<br />\n5世代馬 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">(有用.. 玩左成個星期, 都未捉到隻野生, 多人搶)</span><br />\n<br />\n選擇寵物1隻 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">(有用, 幫手汁野, 有技(要睇咩寵))</span><br />\n<br />\n[活動]未知的染料箱10個<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">幫衫褲鞋武器等等嘅野染色，簡單講就等你同人地著同款衫都會唔同色</span><br />\n<br />\n背包4格<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">(背包做任都有送,, 不過就梗係越多越好)</span><br />\n<br />\n[活動]銀刺繡生活服裝交換券<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">一套幫你提升生活技能嘅衫，拎張券去換，有好幾套比你揀</span><br />\n<br />\n200珍珠<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">(好似寵都買唔到)</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n4. 有咩職業?</span><br />\n暫時開左:<br />\n戰士<br />\n狂戰<br />\n魔女<br />\n遊俠<br />\n馴獸師<br />\n男/女法<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">5. 遊戲有咩玩法??</span><br />\n你鍾意點玩都得.<br />\nPVP , PVE. 公會戰. 攻城戰<br />\n大量生活經營<br />\n買樓(係香港買唔起, 係GAME 度你可以)<br />\n田地<br />\n勞工<br />\n採集<br />\n加工<br />\n煉金<br />\n料理<br />\n馴養<br />\n貿易<br />\n狩獵<br />\n地下貿易<br />\n釣魚<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">6. 有咩攻略網??</span><br />\n<br />\n官方WIKI:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.blackdesert.com.tw/Wiki\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.blackdesert.com.tw%2FWiki&d=JLp0aZeKgaDJxHa8AUPXkWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=98a26df8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.blackdesert.com.tw/Wiki</a><br />\n<br />\n巴哈:<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/A.php?bsn=19017\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FA.php%3Fbsn%3D19017&d=JLp0aZeKgaDJxHa8AUPXkWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=abc9374e\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/A.php?bsn=19017</a><br />\n<br />\n黑沙寶典<br />\n<a href=\"http://bd.youxidudu.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbd.youxidudu.com&d=JLp0aZeKgaDJxHa8AUPXkWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=ac93bb37\" target=\"_blank\">http://bd.youxidudu.com</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">7. 買GAME 方法? 只可以網上買!</span><br />\n<br />\n用 PayPal 或 Mycard +VPN (TW)<br />\nBY 巴打( 去OK買master gift card比錢啦，vpn都唔洗) <br />\n詳細自行google<br />\n<br />\n1001唔開就我開啦"},{"pid":"c7e89134df6703965c14324384c5f3f3f4ae697d","tid":94203,"uid":2751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T05:01:55.000Z","msg":"點解設定唔到代表角色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開完角熄game再開都係唔見有得揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b73d44738272917f76ca62ca723979705182a347","tid":94203,"uid":58850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T05:03:51.000Z","msg":"龜速下載中<br />\n點解有巴打可以2x-3x MB/s<br />\n我就得1MB/s<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"878c19465362bce5cf3543e7d01a57bc544d2ab8","tid":94203,"uid":54176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T05:04:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解設定唔到代表角色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開完角熄game再開都係唔見有得揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲係個柒頭做icon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif